AUTUS Asset Management, LLC 
is a boutique asset management firm dedicated to providing innovative portfolio management solutions 
in today's complex investment environment.  

Services 

Portfolio Management
Autus Asset  Management is an SEC Registered Investment Adviser providing 100% fee-based,  discretionary investment management services for taxable and tax-deferred  portfolios.  We offer our clients many  advantages:

Customized Portfolio Design
Design truly customized portfolios that are well diversified  across asset classes, economic sectors, and individual securities.

Investment Policy Statement (IPS) Preparation
Prepare a hand-tailored IPS to match your tolerance for risk  and meet your needs for income, liquidity and return.

Unbiased, Independent Research
Provide unbiased, independent research that is based on sound  fundamental analysis. Our boutique structure facilitates a nimble and  comprehensive approach for uncovering opportunities.

Risk Management
Manage investment risk by designing portfolios to address our  client’s unique circumstances and the imperfect correlations between asset  classes, economic sectors, and individual securities. 

Tax Sensitivity
Manage portfolios to allow for the  greatest risk-adjusted returns, while actively minimizing tax liabilities.

Retirement Planning
Guide you through the retirement planning process, revise  your plan on a continuous basis and address how best to distribute assets from  your retirement plan accounts.

Concentrated-Wealth Risk Management
Design a program to reduce risk due  to concentrated positions and systematically diversify your portfolio.

Stock Option Strategies
Assist in the understanding of your stock options, develop an  exercise strategy and address the diversification needs.

Client Focused
Understand the unique needs of each client and communicate  with them on a regular basis to review goals, strategies and portfolio  performance.

Experienced Investment Professionals
Work face to face with a knowledgeable and credentialed  investment management team that is exclusively committed to building  customized, efficient portfolios.

Client/Manager Ratio
Maintain an appropriate “client to manager ratio” which  allows our clients to truly realize the benefits of customized portfolio  management.

Cost Efficiency
Minimize portfolio costs through competitive management fees,  low brokerage commissions and moderate asset turnover.

Institutional Support
Utilize industry leading financial institutions, such as  Charles Schwab and Fidelity Investments, to provide asset custody, tax  reporting and trading support.  These  institutions offer account features including on-line access, check writing,  bill paying, wire transfers, systematic withdrawals, margin capability, etc.

  




