​About UsAutus (AW-tus)   is a Latin term meaning: "Grow, Enlarge and Strengthen."We chose this name because it accurately describes our mission of helping our clients reach their unique financial goals by carefully growing and protecting their assets. We pride ourselves on providing customized portfolio management solutions supported by independent research and unparalleled client service. At AUTUS, we honor each client's right to be treated as a unique individual.At AUTUS Asset Management, our investment philosophy is based on modern portfolio theory, which is the cornerstone of portfolio management.  When constructing a client portfolio, our primary consideration is effective asset class utilization, followed by strategic sector allocation, and finally individual security selection.  Each step in our process is made within a well-defined, disciplined framework that maintains independence while emphasizing quality and relative valuation.We are a boutique asset management firm dedicated to providing innovative portfolio management solutions in today's complex investment environment.​Services » Customized Portfolio Design » Investment Policy Statement (IPS) Preparation » Unbiased, Independent Research » Risk Management » Tax Sensitivity » Retirement Planning » Concentrated-Wealth Risk Management » Stock Option Strategies » Client Focused » Client/Manager Ratio » Cost Efficiency » Institutional Support                               










